0 BREW BREWING~
Syntax: brew 'spell name'

This skill can be learned by all classes, but some are more adept at this 
skill than others.  First you must be holding an adequate vial for 
brewing the potion.  There are several criteria before you can sucessfully 
brew a potion.
1. Must be holding vial
2. Must know the spell to be brewed
3. Spell must be a defensive spell or target self only spell
4. Must have adequate mana(4 times the normal mana for the spell)
5. Pass the skill, intelligence and wisdom checks

The max number of spells able to be brewed into one potion is 3, but
they get increasingly more difficult to correctly brew.

Beware a failed potion may explode in your face!
~
0 SCRIBE~
Syntax: scribe 'spell name'

This skill can be learned by all classes, but some are more adept at this 
skill than others.  First you must be holding an adequate parchment for 
scribing the scroll.  There are several criteria before you can sucessfully 
scribe a scroll.
1. Must be holding a parchment
2. Must know the spell to be scribed
3. Must have adequate mana(4 times the normal mana for the spell)
4. Pass the skill, intelligence and wisdom checks

The max number of spells that may be scribed on one scroll is 3, but they
get increasingly difficult to correctly scribe.

Beware a failed scroll may blow up in your face!
~
